L creates multiple parallel dropout networks for each CXR image to evaluate\nuncertainty and thus prevent performance degradation caused by the noise in the\ndata.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 22 Feb 2021 15:13:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-23"}
